Name: NeoSticks
About the game: With the return to the world of Neo. In this game you need to collect a flight on a stick. With the mouse clicks, change the direction of rotation and compute to collect as many sticks as possible. When you feel that you will become a professional, increase the speed or number of sticks. Set highscores and compare them with friends.
